      "text": "ふ～っ、お疲れ様。ロケ楽しかったわね\nこのまま東京に帰る？　それともご飯でも行く？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ good job. Filming was fun\nShall we go back to Tokyo? Or should we go eat?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2999999721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
