      "text": "実は、私行きたい所がありまして\nそこに寄ってから帰りますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ there's a place I want to go\nI'll go back after stopping by there",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0999999721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
