      "text": "そんなに気になるなら怜もついてくればいいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're that curious‚ Rei can come along‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3666668931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうね。そんなに楽しいなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. If it's that much fun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6666668931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
