      "text": "あれ……？　え、ちょっと待って\nあんな崖から紐一本で飛び降りるつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's…? Eh‚ wait a minute\nAre you planning to jump off that cliff with just a string?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4000012437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
