      "text": "ええ、バンジージャンプとはそういうものでしょう？\n高い場所から綺麗な景色を楽しむ一番いい方法ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ isn't that what bungee jumping is?\nIt's the best way to enjoy beautiful views from high up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2666679103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
